\Pi_C
C:=\{w:~w\geq 0\}
\Pi_C(w)=\begin{pmatrix}\tilde{w}_1\\ \vdots \\ \tilde{w}_m \end{pmatrix}
\tilde{w}_i=\begin{cases} w_i &\text{if }w_i\geq 0\\ 0 &\text{else} \end{cases}
